name: SKTestSession.TimeRate
desc: The values for rates of time passing in the test environment.

items.name: case realTime
items.desc: A rate of time in which the test environment runs in real time.

items.name: case monthlyRenewalEveryHour
items.desc: A rate of time in the test environment in which monthly subscriptions renew every hour.

items.name: case monthlyRenewalEveryThirtyMinutes
items.desc: A rate of time in the test environment in which monthly subscriptions renew every thirty minutes.

items.name: case monthlyRenewalEveryFifteenMinutes
items.desc: A rate of time in the test environment in which monthly subscriptions renew every fifteen minutes.

items.name: case monthlyRenewalEveryFiveMinutes
items.desc: A rate of time in the test environment in which monthly subscriptions renew every five minutes.

items.name: case monthlyRenewalEveryThirtySeconds
items.desc: A rate of time in the test environment in which monthly subscriptions renew every thirty seconds.
